Telkom’s Internet services were hit by an outage this morning, with the operator stating it is working on a fix. “We’re currently experiencing an outage on our Internet services. This is our priority and more info to follow. Apologies to all affected,” said Telkom on Facebook. Hundreds of downtime reports were submitted on Down Detector this morning, with many reports posted between 08:00 and 11:00. Telkom has been asked for feedback on the issue.